descript.purpose: To depict the poll locations for election districts, precincts, and legislative subdistricts in Frederick County, Maryland for elections.

idinfo.accconst: Employees of Frederick County, Maryland may access this data. Governmental agencies and private groups or individuals performing contract work for Frederick County may also be provided access to the data by the County's GIS Coordinator.
idinfo.useconst: Frederick County employees have unrestricted use of the data, but are not permitted to distribute the data in its raw format to external groups or individuals without consent from the GIS Coordinator. For governmental agencies and private groups or individuals provided with the data, use is in accordance with Frederick County, Maryland's GIS License Agreement. While efforts have been made to ensure the accuracy of the data, Frederick County accepts no responsibility for errors, omissions, or positional inaccuracies in the data. Frederick County makes no warranty, express or implied, and disclaims all implied warranties of merchantability, integration, title, and fitness of the GIS data for a particular purpose. Reliance on the data is at the risk of the user.

horizpa.horizpar: Positional inaccuracies may exist as a result of the scale at which boundaries were drawn. Boundaries that should be coincident with road and hydrography features at a 1:2400 scale frequently contain positional inaccuracies.

citeinfo.title: 2000 Legislative District Plan As Ordered by the Court of Appeals June 21, 2002

procstep.procdesc:
Below is a copy from election.shp metadata. Polls.shp is probably created by the similar process except that it features point data.
Polygons were constructed in accordance with precinct boundaries as depicted on the source map. The boundaries were digitized along County road and hydrography features created from the County's 1:2400 scale 2000 digital orthophotography. Boundaries were generated at scales ranging from 1:24000 to 1:12000. The Board of Elections reviewed the data for accuracy.

altsys.altenc: Explicit elevation coordinate included with horizontal coordinates

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdef: Precinct number; format is 2 digit election district number - 3 digit precinct number (e.g. 02-001)
